      "review_summary": "The PR adds a Control UI webchat right-click Reply menu, transient composer reply target, preview bar, quoted-Markdown send behavior, styling, and focused chat view tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +257, Tests +121. Total +378 across 9 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the remaining review finding by source inspection: select a reply target, clear chat history via `/clear` or the Clear History button, then send another message and the stale `chatReplyTarget` can still be quoted. The broader linked feature gap is also source-visible on current main because no reply target/menu/preview/send path exists there.",
      "review_followup": "- [P2] A narrow automated repair can clear the new transient reply target in reset paths and add regression tests on the PR branch.",
